      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，三个参与者命名没问题。支付完成后，Payment Gateway把paymentResult通过webhook推给App Builder Extension，不是给前端。然后Extension要主动调前端的getOrderByMaskedCartId接口拿订单数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Payment Gateway",
        "App Builder Extension",
        "paymentResult",
        "webhook",
        "getOrderByMaskedCartId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出三个参与者和第一条消息：Frontend Application发起到Payment Gateway的Payment调用，带上maskedCartId。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend Application",
        "Payment Gateway",
        "Payment",
