      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来加第二条线：Payment Gateway用paymentResult事件或者webhook回调App Builder Extension。这里用虚线箭头表示异步回调。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Payment Gateway",
